ROOTCAUSE: /private/tmp/monobench-work/wt/monogram-gpt-5.3-codex-spark-high-r3-37754/src/bun.js/bindings/BunString.cpp::BunString__toThreadSafe
FIX: In the pointer-swap branch, release the previous impl before overwrite (or equivalently pair it with an `orig.deref()` path) so the old `StringImpl` ownership is transferred exactly once and the refcount remains balanced when isolation creates a new impl.
